    <description>BIZ-65281 Multiplied quantity with Netprice in Previous ACV on Subscription
BIZ-65821 Getting last subscription for migrated contracts in renewal
Modified as part of BIZ-65281 - Calculate Previous ACV value for Migrated Contracts in renewal scenario,
Modified As part of BIZ- 50449,
Modified as part of BIZ-46894, BIZ-47135,
BIZ-50365:  flow should update this Original ACV Change.
RR: Updated to change quote approval status
Code Refactoring
Added checks for update quotes.
BIZ-61797 Tax calculating properly but not included in Renewal Letter document
BIZ-63601 Populate Customer Sales Price per month on Opportunity Product
BIZ-66988 Ramping User Field incorrect during Amend of contract after new sale which has Ramping User as True
BIZ-66416 - Added the Bypass Logic
BIZ-68198 Populate ACV Change for New Sales and NYMY
BIZ-77496 Replace Segment_Months__c with SBQQ__ProrateMultiplier__c in calculateMigratedPrevValue formula
